page.title: 16The new Domesday Researchers
page.content: These chidren worked with Mrs.J. Goffey to complete this survey. {4th.Yrs.}Rebecca Bray,Sarah Lipiatt, Catherine Walker,Ben Brady. {3rd Yrs} Rachel Dunn,Adele Perrott, William Dunn,Ben Moss {2nd Yrs.}Penny Brown,Michael Walker, Daniel Rose,Steven Smallacombe,Peter Lipiatt. {Top Infants }Julie King,Lisa Roberts, Louise Sweet,Thomas Snelgrove,Nina Perrott,David Marden,Richard Dunn. There are not very many of us,and we worked very hard,trying to get every bit of information we could. We found it very interesting and we learned a great deal.We hope you find it as interesting.
